title: MUMBLE_SET_SERVER_ADDRESS
content:
0xE6EB2CD8// MumbleSetServerAddress
void MUMBLE_SET_SERVER_ADDRESS(char* address, int port);Parameters:address: The address of the mumble server.port: The port of the mumble server.Changes the Mumble server address to connect to, and reconnects to the new address.Setting the address to an empty string and the port to -1 will reset to the built in FXServer Mumble Implementation.
